room_title: Escape room "Graveyard Escape" by Sherlock's Escape Rooms in Florence (KY)
room_description:
You’re visiting a grave at an old cemetery across town. Before you know it, darkness is pouring over the graveyard and the sounds of the night surround you. The main gate is locked and you’ve forgotten your way out! By the light of the full moon, you must escape the dead of darkness before the grave keeper returns!
The Graveyard Escape room has limited lighting to enhance the game experience.
